Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.00,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.43,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.94,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,happened way too suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:16.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I was only a nine-year-old child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:21.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware of anything. I didn't know anything. I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:27.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My mother, Empress Marianne of Britannia, was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:31.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Official records indicated that it was done by terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, that is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:39.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It took place at the Aries Imperial Villa, within the imperial capital of Britannia, a place where only royalty live...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:41.90,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How could the terrorists get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have guided them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:52.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's social standing was that of a noble, though she was originally a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:57.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She was an eyesore to the other Imperial princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.82,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There were just too many people who wanted to harm Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.67,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, my mother has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.29,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,"What about it"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:14.34,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Did you request an audience with the Emperor of Britannia just to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:18.13,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Bring in the next one. I do not have the time to play with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:18.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you not protect mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:24.94,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Emperor, the greatest person in this country, are you not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You should have been able to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least you could have visited Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.27,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is the true nature of the imperial family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.97,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,You have been dead since the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:42.85,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you those clothes that you wear on your back right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.57,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Your home, your food, even your life...\NI am the one who gave all of that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.99,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you have not even once truly been alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.55,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you show such insolence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:03.18,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally and I were sent to Japan, which Britannia had been in dispute with over its underground resource, Sakuradite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:09.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We were to be kept as hostages. The two of us were used as diplomatic tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:15.77,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We were sent to the house of the then Prime Minister of Japan, Kururugi Genbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:19.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There, we encountered Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:26.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, those around me were rivals aiming for the throne and the retainers who supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:30.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That was why, to me, Suzaku was the first friend I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally was close to Suzaku too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:38.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we had finally managed to attain peace in this remote, foreign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:39.75,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial calendar. August 10th, 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:49.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia suddenly declared war on Japan. {Original line}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They should have known that Nunnally and I were there! {New line}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:03.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,During the mainland battle, the Britannian army used the Mobile Humanoid Combat Armored Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,the Knightmare Frame, in combat for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:09.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Their power was beyond anything imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:13.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,and the Japanese defense forces were defeated one after another by the Knightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Japan became a territory of the Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:21.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,and had her freedom... rights... and name taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:29.07,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia had taken away even the small bit of peace that Nunnally and I had found.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:31.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:35.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:37.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,going... to break down Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.79,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those without power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:38.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The world shall be judged by us, the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Zero and the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My own personal army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have done well to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:55.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just a while back, my name, my records, and even my heart, were all just lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:02.00,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Back then, I was just a walking corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.71,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.33,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Youngsters are so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.81,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,They have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.07,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Time to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.23,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.60,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch Lamperouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:27.13,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I screamed or struggled, it didn't affect the world at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:28.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I lived on that way by blaming myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.29,Default,Rival,0000,0000,0000,,Waaah! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.62,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Driving along so carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.18,Default,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! That way is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.04,Default,Rival,0000,0000,0000,,Um... was that our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:51.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:53.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:54.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,met that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.49,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.84,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. That's bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.49,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What, what? An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph... all these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.15,Default,Rival,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.47,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.25,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.96,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards, your mission is to find the weapon that the terrorists stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:26.17,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,You are to search within the residence of the Elevens, the Shinjuku ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.19,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Upon discovery, send back the coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If I climb up top now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.39,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A Britannian soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.30,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.15,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,And poison gas on top of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.00,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to talk your way out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm telling you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was Britannia that made the poison gas in the first place, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.82,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then, break apart Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.74,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.67,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.79,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You... so you became a member of the Britannian army?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.09,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.10,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:25.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,My life was put into motion by my encounter with C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:31.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, I thought that I would have to wait a little more before I could start to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.98,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for a student you tried hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.33,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of a Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.25,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,However, your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.66,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,has just ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.63,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.05,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This girl and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to meet my end here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Without being able to do anything... so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.40,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:14.24,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it to end here... do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:19.41,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you have a reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the girl? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.92,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,If you have strength, will you be able to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.08,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,This is a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:32.15,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,In return for power, I want you to grant one of my wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:39.58,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to the contract, you will live as a human, but differ from other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:44.72,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,A different source, a different time, a different life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.35,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the King will make you isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.23,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,If you are prepared for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.48,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The union of Ragnarök.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.82,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Has the legend started yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That contract... I'll bind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:12.85,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,W-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.74,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.58,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I, Lelouch vi Britannia order you bastards to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:19.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.36,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.13,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of who the opponent is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:46.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,it's a power that enforces absolute obedience to any order that is given.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:51.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once they receive the order, there's no way for them to disobey it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:56.77,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, even if it is to end their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've obtained it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to manipulate the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A power that can destroy Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.63,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.74,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,The power I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.14,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Are you unsatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed my schedule forward a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:23.74,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.23,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The plan to destroy Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:30.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would be a little while longer before I could make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.79,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can destroy it with just that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to do this even without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:43.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,C.C., the woman who granted me Geass, appeared in my house for no logical reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:49.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. It'll be bad if she goes outside and leaks out my secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like it won't be possible to shut her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she is someone who took a bullet in the head and still lives on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:03.11,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I need to understand the power of Geass first and destroy Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,In order to use the Geass, one must look directly into the opponents' eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There is no problem penetrating through glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum distance is about 270 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:19.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,After having the Geass cast on them, or when it's in effect, there is a noticeable gap in memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:24.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is thought to be damage caused by the Geass invading the cerebrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.05,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If it has the property of light, then reflection is also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.56,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have studied it a lot in such a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent is an empire which has subdued over a third of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as exercising too much discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.78,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I need to be discreet yet bold at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Speed is essential as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:50.71,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I started to act. I have bet Geass and everything I have on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me... your Knightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:04.96,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.76,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The access number is XG2IG2D4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,R2, launch anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.23,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,B7, a UN Round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Group N, move forward as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.28,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.95,Default,Clobis,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Send Lerus in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Mission number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.74,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,Enclose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.74,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate your firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Are the preparations complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:37.66,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.46,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy isn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.72,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It IS possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it. I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:02.09,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Lelouch. I heard that you had died during the invasion of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.94,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank goodness you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it... the one who killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:20.58,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Prince Schneizel and 2nd Princess Cornelia. They would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They were the masterminds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.14,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,So you really don't know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.59,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't me! I didn't do it! I didn't make anyone do it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.64,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:45.15,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it. Even though we have different mothers, I'm still your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The world cannot be changed with pretty words alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.92,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.48,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, with only one attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.73,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,So this means that the creatures of Area 18 have fallen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:27.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Clovis's successor was the female warrior who pilots her own Knightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The 2nd princess of Britannia, Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:35.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, one of the people who knew the truth behind Mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.23,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act recklessly in Area 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.54,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.29,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I will find you, Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.00,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,to avenge Clovis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.43,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,P2, N3, cut around behind the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.08,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,P2, N3!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:03.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,B1, B5, you guys go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.18,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:10.23,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that we could win against Cornelia's personal unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.86,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.32,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We won't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.28,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.41,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.22,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,B8, status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.45,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There's no status-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,B8!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.07,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are left, report in order from P!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.45,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.73,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,All troops move into formation four.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They were overwhelmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't been much of a game at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.57,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,So it didn't go the same way as Shinjuku, did it, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy wasn't just Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:52.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There was also that white Knightmare that possessed unbelievable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.34,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone escaped but four troops were instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.37,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Number of enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.33,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,One machine, just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.26,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a new model?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.35,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that type bef-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:04.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:14.79,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What? It can block bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.77,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.65,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,These terrorists are so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's only one machine and they can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.61,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the guy... the one who's messing with my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A mere pilot like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:51.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.76,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. I need to eject here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:11.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There's also that man who's behind the Britannian Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.94,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,People are... not equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:19.26,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are born fleet of foot... those who are born beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:24.57,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Those who's parents are poor... those who have weak bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:30.88,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Birth, growth and talent, all humans... are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:35.60,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, people are born to be different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.46,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,That is why people fight and compete with one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.87,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,From there, evolution takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:47.15,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Inequality is not an evil. Equality itself is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.23,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,What of the EU which made their policies equal for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.77,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,They have become mere spectators of a mob-ruled government!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.78,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The Chinese Federation, which made its citizens equal, is full of negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.59,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,But we, Britannia, are not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:06.54,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,We fight, compete and continue to evolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:12.03,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Compete, take, possess, control!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.55,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that lies the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.67,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:34.77,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(0,4600)}All Hail Britannia! All Hail Britannia! All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.50,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.47,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia is large and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible to win this battle with just the Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I created the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Fear us or seek us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:45.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We are... the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:50.43,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Order of the Black Knights, are allies of all those who hold no weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.25,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Be it Elevens or Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:20:01.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese Liberation Front used underhanded tactics, used Britannian civilians as hostages, and killed them in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was a meaningless act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.60,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we have punished them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Clovis, the previous Governor-general, was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He massacred Elevens who possessed no weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:18.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to see these kinds of cruel acts, which is why I punished him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:25.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, the act of the strong completely and utterly killing the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.03,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who are prepared to be killed should be allowed to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the Hoteljacking incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:38.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,the world's attention has been on Zero and the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:46.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Disgust, bewilderment, fear, adoration, surprise, ridicule, delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone feels differently about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:55.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To the ghettos, we're heroes. To the settlements, we're villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:59.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right; there isn't a need for everyone to support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:05.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Loyalty can only be built up when one side goes through a fair number of challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.90,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not enough to drag that man out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.23,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:22.69,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,You've been coming home late recently. Are you gambling again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.34,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley-san is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:28.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've already stopped doing that. Gambling, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.42,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.47,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:37.10,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't easy for us to meet up with Suzaku-san again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.35,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,If we could go back to how it was before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.30,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Back to how it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.22,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, in order to make that happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.38,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:30.33,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have a present for those who tune in tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:34.33,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A set consisting of the CD of the opening theme song by FLOW, COLORS,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.17,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,a clear file specially produced for the show, a calling card, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:41.54,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,a figure of me with my mask off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:42.79,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This present will be given to 10 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:47.48,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's only available to subscribers of the MBS cellphone service!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.11,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from I, Lelouch vi Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.74,FLOW Ad,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Subscribe to it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.21,0:23:53.95,FLOW Ad,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:23:59.55,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How fortunate, heaven is on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.79,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have realized that Cornelia's weakness was one of the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:04.79,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That weakness called Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:08.58,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for me and the Order of the Black Knights to launch a counterattack
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:14.48,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,against this world that has imprisoned me, and against my own frozen heart.
